title: Cee's Tizzy, sire of Tiznow, dies aged 28
text: Cee's Tizzy, sire of Tiznow, dies aged 28 Wednesday, 21 October 2015 (8 minutes ago) Cee's Tizzy, the sire of dual Breeders' Cup Classic winner and top sire Tiznow, has been put down due to the infirmities of old age.
